20:43.742 --> 20:45.994
♪ BA-BA, BA-BA ♪

20:46.078 --> 20:50.958
♪ ♪

20:51.041 --> 20:53.293
♪ BA-BA, BA-BA ♪

20:53.377 --> 20:55.253
♪ BA-BA, BA-BA ♪

21:04.012 --> 21:05.347
